<hr><p><a href="https://crowdfundiing.typeform.com/to/CC8XFvbi"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-188315 size-large" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/ac5b2f1f116a7335e0affab85492f429-560x293.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="293" srcset="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/ac5b2f1f116a7335e0affab85492f429-560x293.jpg 560w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/ac5b2f1f116a7335e0affab85492f429-350x183.jpg 350w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/ac5b2f1f116a7335e0affab85492f429-768x402.jpg 768w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/ac5b2f1f116a7335e0affab85492f429-30x16.jpg 30w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/ac5b2f1f116a7335e0affab85492f429.jpg 1201w" sizes="(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px"></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>全新计画《科学生线上学习平台》</strong><strong><a href="https://crowdfundiing.typeform.com/to/CC8XFvbi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">问卷</a>募集中！<a href="https://crowdfundiing.typeform.com/to/CC8XFvbi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">填答</a>就有机会获得精美好礼！</strong></p>
