<li>Howard DM. The Vocal Tract Organ: A New Musical Instrument Using 3-D Printed Vocal Tracts. <i>J Voice</i>. 2018;32(6):660-667. <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29111337/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">doi:10.1016/j.jvoice.2017.09.014</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2020/01/23/science/mummy-voice.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Mummy Speaks! Hear Sounds From the Voice of an Ancient Egyptian Priest</a> <em>The New York Times</em></li>
